{"tid":1267722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回帶撚] 茶客涉誤殺奶茶叔　案轉高院審訊","createTime":"2019-06-30T04:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T04:45:12.000Z","uid":49647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1033d6485a22bad19f788a10abbfce28c860062f","tid":1267722,"uid":49647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:41:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160524/mobile/bkn-20160524161238408-0524_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20160524%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20160524161238408-0524_00822_001.html&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=2547a325\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20160524/mobile/bkn-20160524161238408-0524_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n年近六旬「奶茶叔」去年在茶餐廳飲奶茶時要加糖，被指將「舔完」試味的私匙，插落公用糖罐舀沙糖，同枱一名貨車男司機不滿要食其「口水尾」，雙方爭執，期間司機涉嫌將「奶茶叔」推跌落地，令對方腦部大量出血，昏迷數月後身亡。涉案司機梁寶鈿被控一項誤殺罪，案件今日在觀塘法院再訊，被告毋須答辯，押後至6月30日轉介東區法院，以作交付高等法院審訊的程序，被告期間還押。 <br />\n<br />\n46歲被告被控去年10月10日，在順天邨天權樓的萬順茶餐廳外，非法殺死58歲男子黃文權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190628/s00001/1561688724915/推跌六旬漢奪命-青年涉謀殺還押7月3日再訊\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190628%2Fs00001%2F1561688724915%2F%E6%8E%A8%E8%B7%8C%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E6%BC%A2%E5%A5%AA%E5%91%BD-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E6%B6%89%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC7%E6%9C%883%E6%97%A5%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=a39d01e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190628%2Fs00001%2F1561688724915%2F%E6%8E%A8%E8%B7%8C%E5%85%AD%E6%97%AC%E6%BC%A2%E5%A5%AA%E5%91%BD-%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E6%B6%89%E8%AC%80%E6%AE%BA%E9%82%84%E6%8A%BC7%E6%9C%883%E6%97%A5%E5%86%8D%E8%A8%8A&h=899ac262\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190628/s00001/1561688724915/推跌六旬漢奪命-青年涉謀殺還押7月3日再訊</a><br />\n<br />\n點解一件就誤殺，一件就謀殺。"},{"pid":"00b5ca48ffe52bca1e0d68a669588fe35a3d4772","tid":1267722,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:45:12.000Z","msg":"搵唔到證據係謀殺先會改誤殺，好似係"}]}